            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "Is",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
            "text": "betrayed.",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "—The tense, as in St. Matthew, is present, “is at this moment being betrayed.”",
            "children": []
