        "text": " an interesting note in Field’s ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Otium Nor",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The meaning is: I have conquered in the struggle; I need your sympathy no longer; you may sleep now if you will.",
        "children": []
